    ns1:otherInformation """Due to the size of the Laboratory rooms, the maximum number of students being assisted for each professor at the Laboratory sessions will be 12.

The subject is related to SDG7 and SDG9.

TRIBUNAL:
President: Nuria Martín Piris
Vocal: Daniel Barba Cancho
Secretary: Laura Córdova González
Substitute: Rodrigo Santos Güemes"""@es ;
